- async web framework.

Create new project steps:
==========================

-> open inteliij & select create new project
-> install Ktor plugin into intelliij
-> select gradle/maven , and go with default settings
-> Project created

QuickIntro:
===========

-> It will have module function called from Application class.
-> Ktor application class is a program listening to one or more ports and containing module with installed features.
-> Application composed of different modules.
-> Module contain the application logic.
-> Features are installed to the module to provide additional functionality such as logging authentication.
-> Routes are one of the feature to simplify request handling.


